{"tid":2070872,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣國民黨學壞了，聲言拒絕一國兩制。去中國化成台灣朝野共識。","createTime":"2020-06-19T12:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T12:42:25.000Z","uid":48040,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"963e973d76192c3abbc0c303883f2c35a997c1d6","tid":2070872,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"國民黨敗選之後，痛定思痛，推動改革。但改革成果原來就是抄襲民進黨的綱領和理念，包括拒絕一國兩制，保障自由民主人權。不知道國民黨有沒有付版權費給民進黨呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">林鄭月娥令「拒絕一國兩制」成為台灣社會的一致共識，不知道這算不算民族罪人呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n中國國民黨改革委員會周五(6月19日)召開大會，提出兩岸新論述之建議案，力圖扭轉&ldquo;親中&rdquo;包袱，雖然仍保留&ldquo;九二共識&rdquo;的既定立場，但明確拒絕一國兩制並支持香港的民主，也新創四大支柱：堅持中華民國主權、保障自​​由民主人權、維護台灣安全優先、創造雙贏共享繁榮，以期建構和平穩定的台海新關係。國民黨主席江啟臣在閉幕致詞時將此奠基在主權、民主人權、安全和繁榮的四大支柱定調為九二Plus，<span style=\"color: orange;\">否認國民黨在兩岸立場上向民進黨靠攏，嚴斥&ldquo;小綠&rdquo;的標籤</span>。<br />\n<br />\n不過，中國學者說，非常不樂見國民黨在正式論述裡拒絕一國兩制、且支持香港的民主，這將嚴重打擊國共兩黨未來可能互動和對話的基礎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/kmt-releases-new-china-policy-clearly-states-rejection-china-one-country-two-systems-framework-20200619/5469125.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fkmt-releases-new-china-policy-clearly-states-rejection-china-one-country-two-systems-framework-20200619%2F5469125.html&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=cdc7f51b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/kmt-releases-new-china-policy-clearly-states-rejection-china-one-country-two-systems-framework-20200619/5469125.html</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wlXPiafyjLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwlXPiafyjLc&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=142aa437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wlXPiafyjLc</a>"},{"pid":"f4472f4c948d5da624e59abf22a7197ec30322eb","tid":2070872,"uid":113187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl